title: 233 The Immortal Joggers
description:
MATERIAL: 100% Cotton.

FABRIC WEIGHT: 360 GSM.

FIT: Relaxed.

DESIGN: Made with soft fleece cotton and an oversized fitting, the immortal joggers are here to stay. Rock the baggy looks at the gym or outside. The Young Ambitious Club print on the left leg represents the mentality of our core audience. The hunger of the hunting eagle and the blossom of the roses all show the immortality of our dream. The dream to succeed.

MODEL: The model in the first photo is wearing a size Medium. Weight: 175lb Height: 5'9.

WHY WE MADE THIS: These are probably the coolest YoungLA Joggers we have made to date!! The prints and the fit of the joggers just differentiate them from anything we have made before! We are extremely excited about this project and looking forward to the direction these joggers will take the brand!
